{
  "texts": [
    "This advancement notably enhances the perceived quality of high-frequency human body details.In the preprocessing phase, four critical techniques were utilized.",
    "Each method was integrated and executed consecutively to ensure optimal input quality for the virtual try-on model.",
    "Central to the FITMI application's user appeal is its sophisticated recommendation system.",
    "The application allows users to see themselves in desired outfits and intelligently recommends garments based on individual style preferences.",
    "This personalization is further enhanced by FITMI's ability to suggest complementary items, effectively simulating a personalized shopping assistant."
  ]
